    "The remaining 286 participants-our final sample-self-identified as 51.0% female, 46.52% male, and 2.8% other or unanswered; 7.0% Hispanic or Latinx; 76.6% White, 13.6% Black, 6.6% Asian, and 5.5% other or unanswered (ethnic and racial categories were non-exclusive); and with a mean age of 46.76 (SD = 16.33).",
